## Project Overview
This project demonstrates CRUD operations on a Book using springboot and Mongodb


## Prerequisites
- Java 21.0.6
- Maven 3.9.9
- Docker 28.1.1
- Spring Boot 3.5.3

## 1. Running MongoDB with Docker for this project:

docker run -d --name books-mongo -p 27017:27017 -e MONGO_INITDB_ROOT_USERNAME=root -e MONGO_INITDB_ROOT_PASSWORD=secret mongo:7


## 2. Build the app and run tests:

mvn clean package

## 3. Run the app:

mvn spring-boot:run


## 4. OpenAPI Documentation
After running the app, access the API documentation and interact with the App at:
http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui/index.html
